Installation

    git clone https://github.com/jlisinski/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symbolic links

    ln -s dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s dotfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Installing Pathogen as git submodule

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule add https://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen.git pathogen
    mkdir autoload
    ln -s ~/.vim/pathogen/pathogen.vim pathogen.vim
    
Get submodules

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update



